        <div class="agreement" style="display: block;">
            <div id="listThree">

                <div class="Section0" style="layout-grid:15.6000pt;"><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:center;mso-outline-level:2;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:13.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:18.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">实盘点买人与实盘出借人合作协议</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:13.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:18.0000pt;"></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">重要提示：</font> </span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">本协议签订前，您须认真阅读平台提供的《证券交易风险提示书》及《实盘点买人参与证券交易合作涉及费用及资费标准》，您阅读签署前述协议并提交确认后，方能签署本协议。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">甲方（实盘点买人）：</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">乙方（信息撮合服务平台）：</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">丙方（实盘出借人）：</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">鉴于甲方有操盘股票交易账户获利的需求，丙方亦同意提供股票交易账户，双方有意成立委托操盘关系，并授权乙方作为信息撮合服务平台达成合作。在乙方平台的撮合下，甲方实盘点买人（资金需求方）发出交易买卖指令，通过丙方实盘出借人（账户出借方）在国内正规证券公司开具的股票账户，完成交易沪深证券交易所二级市场的股票交易。根据《中华人民共和国合同法》、《电子签名法》等法律法规，经各方公平平等协商，就证券交易合作事宜订立如下协议，以兹共守：</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;mso-outline-level:3;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">一、专有术语</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">1.1实盘点买人：即点买操盘人，指通过平台注册并完成实名认证、银行卡绑定开户的用户，作为实盘出借人的交易合作方，通过实盘出借人出借证券实盘交易账户及资金，进行完成沪深证券交易所二级市场股票交易的自然人。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">1.2信息撮合服务平台：作为一家依法成立并有效存续的有限责任公司，面向平台注册用户（实盘点买人）提供包括但不限于沪深证券交易所二级市场交易合作信息发布、借贷双方信息撮合（账户出借方和资金需求方）、交易指令通讯、交易风控管理、借贷双方盈亏结算、交易清结算、资金安全托管（由支付机构提供）等服务的线上中介服务平台。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">1.3实盘出借人：作为实盘点买人（资金需求方）的交易合作方，负责在国内正规证券公司开设股票账户，根据实盘点买人交易买卖指令提供自有资金借给实盘点买人进行交易的自然人或法人。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">1.4点买金额：指实盘点买人买入单支股票的预借款总额，一般少于或等于实际市场买入的等值股票金额，以整数（单位：万元）展示。具体收费应参照《实盘点买人参与证券交易合作涉及费用及资费标准》及平台最新公布为准。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">1.5履约保证金：即实盘点买人向乙方平台提交的用于承担交易亏损赔付义务的资金。该笔资金一经提交，即被冻结。在投资期间，由平台根据实盘点买人交易情况对其盈亏及时进行结算。实盘点买人在平台结算后，可提取保证金。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">1.6点买：指实盘点买人通过乙方平台发出股票买入指令（选择股票，选择点买金额，购买数量，设置止盈止损等），最终指令实际下达给实盘出借人。买入指令为即时委托买入，指实盘点买人发出交易指令所在时点起，以即时市价买入指定数量的股票。（点买成交价以实际市场成交价格为准，不含手续费）</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">1.7点卖：指实盘点买人发出点卖指令。点卖指令为即时卖出。即时卖出为实盘点买人发出交易指令所在时点起，以即时市价卖出指定数量的股票（点卖成交价含印花税及卖出佣金）。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">1.8触发止盈/止损：当交易盈亏触发（多于或等于）指定的止盈止损位时，投资者有关持仓股票会被强制平仓。由于市场波动，交易数据传输，网络延迟以及移动端设备网络信号等不确定因素，可能导致最终卖出价格超过止盈止损位，此时应以实际市场成交为准,该成交结果应当由实盘点买人承受。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">1.9持仓时间：股票属T+1/D模式，即当日买入，次日才能卖出的规则。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">1.10递延费：实盘点买人在满足递延条件的前提下，继续持有股票，需缴纳点买金额的递延费用，具体收费应参照《实盘点买人参与证券交易合作涉及费用及资费标准》及平台最新公布为准。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">1.11递延条件：</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">a、持仓股票不在平台黑名单中，既不是高风险股，也不是即将停盘股。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">b、持仓股票满足（浮动盈亏+履约保证金）/点买金额&gt;6%（数据仅供参考，实际以平台实际最新公布为准。）</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">c、截止T日14:50:00，实盘点买人余额充足，足够支付下一交易日的递延费，默认递延。（如发现实盘点买人余额不足或部分不足，系统优先以点买时间先后进行平仓，直到实盘点买人够付递延费或全部策略卖出。）</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">1.12支付机构：指平台委托的为平台用户提供资金划转、查询、结算等支付服务的非金融支付机构。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">1.13平台账户：指面向实盘点买人提供第三方交易资金结算服务的专项账户或用户资金的托管账户。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">1.14交易时段：指实盘出借人授权实盘点买人交易的时间段。具体买入时间为上午9:30:00-11:25:00，下午13:00:00-14:59:00（沪市），下午13:00:00-14:56:00（深市）；卖出时间为T+1/D上午9:30:00-11:25:00，下午13:00:00-14:50:00（数据仅供参考，具体以平台实际最新公布为准）。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">1.15最大持仓截止时间：指平台公布的最大持仓期限：20天（含前2日），具体以平台实际公布时间为准。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">1.16浮动盈亏：计算结果为正值（含零）时即为浮盈金额，计算结果为负值时即为浮亏金额。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;mso-outline-level:3;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">二、合作模式</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">2.1甲方作为实盘点买人（资金需求方），利用乙方平台提供的交易软件完成注册、开立账户，按平台的要求注入保证金。甲方通过提供保证金取得丙方股票交易账户的实际点买操作权限，且承担操盘风险，盈亏自负。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">2.2乙方作为信息撮合服务平台，提供交易软件给甲方进行点买交易，确保甲方每笔交易指令下达给丙方，丙方以闲散资金进行接单下单到沪深证券交易所二级市场完成交易。同时乙方对甲方注入的保证金进行监管，为甲、丙双方资金往来交易的盈亏清算、结算等服务。甲方须知乙方属提供居间服务的第三方平台，利润来源于为甲方提供线上国内证券交易居间服务，乙方不承担甲方操盘的实际盈亏。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">2.3 丙方作为实盘出借人（账户出借方），在国内正规证券公司开设股票交易账户，并提交该交易账户与乙方交易软件互联互通，并且根据甲方发布交易指令提供借款作为甲方交易国内股票的杠杆资金。甲方须知丙方属仅出借向甲方提供交易账户及实际操盘资金权限给甲方进行交易，不参与实盘点买人的实际操盘。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;mso-outline-level:3;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">三、实盘点买人（甲方）权利与义务（补充细则）</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">3.1实盘点买人负责提供本次交易合作的交易策略，即买入指令\平仓指令。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">3.2实盘点买人应在本协议1.14、1.15约定的交易时段内向实盘出借人发出买入指令。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">3.3实盘点买人应在本协1.14、1.15约定的交易时段内向实盘出借人发出平仓指令。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">3.4实盘点买人应按照平台（乙方）公布的履约保证金费用，委托平台系统冻结履约保证金，作为履行交易亏损赔付义务的保证。具体收费应参照《实盘点买人参与证券交易合作涉及费用及资费标准》。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">3.5实盘点买人应按照平台（乙方）公布的建仓费用及递延费，通过向平台支付建仓费及递延费，以支付乙方的信息服务费、乙方代第三方支付平台收取的手续费以及乙方代实盘出借人（丙方）收取的相关补偿费用（包括但不限于买入交易佣金、过户费、证管费、经手费、资金占用费）实盘出借人。具体收费应参照《实盘点买人参与证券交易合作涉及费用及资费标准》。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">3.6实盘点买人应授权平台（乙方）系统在交易亏损时按本协议相关约定，从冻结的履约保证金中向实盘出借人（丙方）支付应承担的亏损赔付款。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">3.7在平台（乙方）撮合服务下，实盘点买人与实盘出借人双方约定：实盘点买人以其所冻结的履约保证金承担交易盈亏赔付时，如交易亏损大于用户冻结履约保证金数额，超过部分由实盘出借人（丙方）承担；如交易盈利，实盘点买人获得盈利部分的90%，并补偿实盘出借人（丙方）获得盈利部分的10%。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">3.8实盘点买人持仓的股票，需满足1.11递延条件及未触发止盈/止损的前提下，可继续持仓，否则视为实盘点买人发出即时提交平仓指令给实盘出借人（丙方），实盘点买人对此不持有异议。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">3.9实盘点买人购买的股票原则上应业绩优良、流通股本规模适度、流动性好。甲方实盘点买人购买股票要按照以下条件：</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">1）不得投资于S、ST、*ST、S*ST、SST，以及被交易所特别处理的股票；</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><br></span><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">2）不得投资于权证类可以T+0交易的证券，不得用于新股申购，也不得用于基金的申购、认购、赎回；</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><br></span><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">3）不得投资于首日上市60个交易日内的新股（或复牌首日股票）等当日不设涨跌停板限制的股票；</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><br></span><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">4）不得投资盘中涨幅≥8％或跌幅≤-8％的股票，直至股票涨跌幅回落到（-8％,+8%）区间，实盘点买人的点买指令方可生效；</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><br></span><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">5）点买金额50万以上主板（含中小板）单只股票不得超过账户总资产的50%（50万或以下不受限制）；</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><br></span><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">6）点买金额100万以上创业板单只股票不得超过账户总资产的20%（100万或以下不受限制）；</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><br></span><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">7）单只股票持仓总市值不得超过该股前5个交易日日均成交额的30%；</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><br></span><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">8）单股最大持仓点买金额为100万，超出就无法再点买该股；</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><br></span><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">9）超过当天可点买次数，无法点买；</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><br></span><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">10）不得进行坐庄、对敲、接盘、大宗交易、内幕信息等违反股票交易法律法规及证券公司规定的交易；</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><br></span><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">11）不得购买其他被纳入《股票黑名单》的高风险股票；</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><br></span><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">如按照收盘价计算，甲方实盘点买人在某一交易日违反上述任一约定时，应在第二个交易日上午</font>10:00前卖出该支股票或降低至规定比例之下，否则乙方平台有权以任何可以成交的价格卖出违反本条约之类别股票。</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">&nbsp;</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">3.10实盘点买人购买股票如若发生停牌，点买人必须缴纳停牌期间的递延费，具体收费应参照《实盘点买人参与证券交易合作涉及费用及资费标准》，直至复盘卖出结算；若停牌期间不缴纳递延费，一旦累计递延费超过实盘点买人所提交的履约保证金，视为实盘点买人放弃该停牌股票的权益，实盘出借人则该账户实际点买操作权限全部转归丙方实盘出借人所有，股票的盈亏亦全部转归丙方负责，与甲方实盘点买人无关实盘出借人，实盘点买人对此不持有异议。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">3.11实盘点买人购买股票如若发生分红、送股、转增等股利政策，乙方平台以降低实盘点买人该股票成本价的形式体现权益。届时该股票的分红、送股、转增等权益与实盘点买人无关，所有权归丙方实盘出借人所有，实盘点买人对此不持有异议。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;mso-outline-level:3;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">四、乙方（平台）的权利与义务</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">4.1为实盘点买人提供交易软件、保证金监管和结算服务。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">4.2有权监管股票交易账户的运作，针对实盘点买人的交易进行丙方账户的管理和风险控制。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">4.3收取平台信息技术服务费用，服务费用详见乙方平台、丙方实盘出借人双方签署的《国内证券交易合作伙伴协议》。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">4.4交易时段盘中，当交易股票浮盈金额≥触发止盈额时或|浮亏金额|≥触发止损额时，视同实盘点买人（甲方）即时发出平仓指令，乙方有权自动执行该指令，实盘点买人对此不持有异议。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">4.5交易时段收盘前10分钟-15分钟，当实盘点买人（甲方）交易股票不满足1.11递延条件情况下，视为实盘点买人已发出即时平仓指令，并自动执行该平仓指令，实盘点买人对此不持有异议。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">4.6实盘点买人（甲方）必须在持仓截止时间（乙方平台公布时间为准）前发出平仓指令，否则乙方视为实盘点买人已发出了即时平仓指令，并自动执行该平仓指令，实盘点买人对此不持有异议。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">4.7甲方发出买入指令后，交易股票在交易时段盘中处于指令以外价格区间时，乙方有权不接受并不执行实盘点买人（甲方）的买入指令，直至交易股票脱离上述价格区间时，乙方方可执行实盘点买人的买入指令。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;mso-outline-level:3;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">五、实盘出借人（丙方）权利与义务（补充细则）</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">5.1实盘出借人负责提供用于本次交易合作的账户和资金。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">5.2实盘出借人承担本次交易所属证券公司产生的买入佣金、过户费、证管费、经手费。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">5.3实盘点买人（甲方）和实盘出借人（丙方）共同委托本平台（乙方）按照以上规则对本次交易合作进行清结算，甲方和丙方同意以本平台的清结算数据作为对甲方盈亏分配的依据。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">5.4实盘出借人享有在本协议3.5、3.6、3.7、3.10、3.11约定的权利与义务。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;mso-outline-level:3;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">六、交易清结算和盈亏分配约定</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">6.1点买成交价：买入成交价来自交易所回报数据，不含手续费。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">6.2点卖成交价：平仓成交价来自交易所回报数据，含印花税、卖出佣金。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">6.3交易盈亏：计算结果为正值（含零）时即为交易盈利，计算结果为负值时即为交易亏损。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">6.4交易费：（印花税+卖出佣金）：印花税、卖出佣金由实盘点买人承担，平台（乙方）在实盘点买人卖出持仓股票时，均摊到点卖成本价的形式体现。计算公式为：交易费=实盘卖出价格×卖出股票股数×2‰ ，不足一万按照20元一笔收取。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">6.5盈利分配：平台清结算除去印花税、卖出佣金之后，实盘点买人享有本次交易的盈利部分90%，实盘出借人享有本次交易的盈利部分10%。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">6.6亏损赔付：实盘点买人承担本次交易亏损。实盘点买人以冻结履约保证金额承担交易亏损，超过履约保证金部分由实盘账户出借方（丙方）承担。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;mso-outline-level:3;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">七、特别约定</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">7.1各方约定从实盘点买人（甲方）通过乙方平台发出交易指令时点起，至国内实盘账户委托下单成交时点止，两时点间隔不超过60秒即为即时买入／即时平仓的时间范畴。另外，从实盘点买人（甲方）发出交易指令被平台（乙方）确认时点起，至交易指令成交时点止，两时点时间间隔不超过75秒。如因网络等原因造成交易成交结果回报时间延迟的，以实际交易成交时间为准。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">7.2甲、丙双方授权平台（乙方）系统依据平台的清结算数据，通过双方在平台系统冻结的履约保证金向甲方进行盈利分配款或亏损赔付款的划拨。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">7.3因不可抗力导致平台（乙方）系统故障，引发交易指令通讯失败或交易指令执行失败，乙方不承担责任，甲、丙双方约定以平台系统恢复就近时间重新执行并以执行的最终结果进行交易清结算。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">7.4为了不影响app运行速度和数据量过大导致缓存增加，平台（乙方）每一个月会对业务数据进行清空，实盘点买人（甲方）需自行备份，平台（乙方）不承担由此导致的任何责任。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;mso-outline-level:3;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">八、协议的签订、成立、生效与法律适用</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">8.1签订：本协议由实盘出借人（丙方）和实盘点买人（甲方）通过平台（乙方）以网络页面点击确认的方式签署。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">8.2成立：本协议自实盘点买人（甲方）或实盘出借人（丙方）签订本协议之日（以两者孰后签订时间为准）成立。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">8.3生效：本协议一经签订即生效。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">8.4本协议的成立、生效、履行、解释及纠纷解决，适用中华人民共和国大陆地区法律（不包括冲突法）。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">8.5 三方之间因本协议发生任何纠纷或争议，首先应友好协商解决；协商不成的，任何一方均有权将纠纷或争议提交至有管辖权的人民法院管辖。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;mso-outline-level:3;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">九、其他</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">9.1 本协议项下所有的通知均可通过重要页面公告、电子邮件或常规的信件传送等方式进行，该等通知于发送之日视为已送达收件人。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">9.2 本协议所有条款的标题仅为阅读方便，本身并无实际涵义，不能作为本协议涵义解释的依据。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">9.3 本协议条款无论因何种原因部分无效，其余条款仍有效，对各方具有约束力。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;mso-outline-level:3;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="宋体">十、特别声明</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">10.1甲方声明：本人已确认了解本协议、《证券交易风险提示书》及《实盘点买人参与证券交易合作涉及费用及资费标准》的内容，并且深入了解和认识到本投资项目可能蕴含的市场风险，也愿意承担由于市场风险而带来的投资损失，签署本协议完全是本人真实意思表示。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">10.2乙方声明：我方系国内成立的一家依法成立并有效存续的有限责任公司，我公司所提供的交易软件能够满足投资者便捷观看相关国内股票行情，下达交易指令、提取保证金等操作；我方保证该软件能够与相关国内股票行情同步进行，保证实盘点买人（甲方）通过我方提供的交易软件进行的交易为真实交易；保证本协议所述均为真实的，如果因所述与事实不符造成实盘点买人损失的，我方愿意承担实盘点买人的损失和有关行政、刑事法律责任。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:5.0000pt;mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:left;background:rgb(255,255,255);"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">10.3丙方声明：我方系证券交易账户合法持有人，保证本协议所述均为真实的，我方与乙方系战略合作关系，如果因所述与事实不符造成实盘点买人（甲方）损失的，我方愿意与乙方承担实盘点买人的损失。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"></span></p></div><!--EndFragment-->
